      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 67,
      "message": "We are creating a collector provider which creates a single routing per config. Every time a clients connects the invoke is called and a new router is created overriding the previous one. The close is called only for the latest client. Is it a desired behavior?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2683,
        "name": "Piotr Jaszczyk",
