      "file_path": "sources/hv-collector-core/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/impl/Router.kt",
      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 89,
      "message": "I'd rather have these sinks lazily-created. For now it may stay as is (as we have only one data stream expected). But we should create a task for the improvement, don't you think?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2683,
        "name": "Piotr Jaszczyk",
